The paper discusses the implementation of a fog computing system in the context of medical IoT, which involves networking, communication, and data processing. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also addresses security and privacy issues, which could fall under cs.CY (Cryptography and Security) and cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of fog computing in healthcare, which could be relevant to cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) and cs.SE (Software Engineering).
